text: I was at a festival where all the food vendors were grossly overpriced but was lucky to see Los Tacos Mariachis Food Truck, which was one of the only vendors not price gauging, offered the best value out of over 9 food trucks in attendance, and had great house made green and red hot sauces! Mariachis Food Truck serves 5 kinds of tacos including Quesa birria, Pollo, Carne Asada, chorizo, and veggie, loaded nachos, chicken Quesadillas, steak Quesadillas, and tres leches. The Quesa birria shredded beef tacos had an amazing flavor and a savory dipping sauce. 10/10The Carne Asada Steak tacos had a great marinade and paired well with the red and green hot sauces. 10/10 Los Tacos Mariachis Food Truck staff says they will be setting up a permanent spot off Adamo drive, 2 blocks East of US 301 Highway at 8505 East Adamo Drive, in the Brandon Area of Tampa. If you're in the Seffner or Brandon area of Tampa and craving some authentic birria tacos, definitely check out Los Tacos Mariachis Food Truck!
name: Brian

text: Very good.  The salsa is awesome. Good flavor. Great atmosphere and clean.  The quesabirria amazing.  Loved it definitely will be back
